    "careers-about": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "About Us",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "para_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Since 2004 TRENDYGOLF have been answering the question \"Where can we buy this from?\"</p>"
          }
        },
        "para_2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Inspired by Jesper Parnevik's famous style, our founders scoured the internet to find where they could get their hands on the look. It was then they discovered J.LINDEBERG but found no way to buy it. That's when TRENDYGOLF was born, becoming a one-stop-shop for golfers worldwide to shop the looks of the most famous golfers.</p>"
          }
        },
        "para_3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Since 2004 the company has spread accross the globe, boasting offices in both the UK and USA. But the mission remains the same, provide the latest golf fashion & accessories that the top players are wearing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "para_4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>TRENDYGOLF is not only aimed at the fashionable golfer, but is an institution that brings the latest designs from the most sought after designers to the forefront of fashion, both on and off the course.</p>"
          }
        },
        "para_5": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>It's all about confidence and with TRENDYGOLF as your personal stylist, you'll look your best wherever your round takes you.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading",
